{
  "sections": {
    "pf-87b34d07": {
      "type": "pf-87b34d07",
      "settings": {
        "pf_845fcebc_value": "You can earn points through various ways of engaging with DELLA. The primary methods include:\n<br><br><strong>1.Making Purchases:</strong>&nbsp;Earn 1 point for every $1 spent on the official website or app.\n<br><br><strong>2.Account &amp; Social Engagement:</strong>&nbsp;Earn welcome points by completing your profile, following our social media accounts, and subscribing to our emails.\n<br><br><strong>3.Sharing Your Experience:&nbsp;</strong>Earn points by submitting product reviews or sharing approved brand content on social media platforms (e.g., Facebook, Instagram, TikTok).\n<br><br><strong>4.DIY Projects:&nbsp;</strong>Earn DIY points by uploading content of your installation process that meets our standards.<br><br><strong>5.Referring Friends:&nbsp;</strong>Earn points when your friends complete a purchase using your referral.\n<br><br><strong>6.Participating in Activities:</strong>&nbsp;Join community events and seasonal challenges.<br><br><strong>Important Notes:</strong>\n<br>&nbsp;Point rewards for specific activities are set by DELLA and are subject to change. Please always refer to the latest information on our official website or activity pages.\n<br><br>Points are only awarded for eligible actions completed&nbsp;after&nbsp;these Program rules have been fully implemented. We do not retroactively award points for past orders.<br><br>Members registered before the Program launch received initial points for completing account setup and initial tasks.<br>",
        "pf_d8fd4b5e_value": "Yes. The Program features a VIP tier system where you automatically advance to higher tiers based on your&nbsp;<strong>historical cumulative point</strong> total, unlocking more benefits.\nFor detailed point requirements and complete benefit details for each tier, please visit:&nbsp;https://dellahome.com/pages/della-rewards-program<br><strong><br>Tier Overview:\n<br><br>Bronze/Silver (Entry Level):&nbsp;</strong>Gain access to the DELLA member community.<strong>\n<br><br>Silver (3,500+ points):&nbsp;</strong>Earn points on purchases and redeem DELLA merchandise.<strong>\n<br><br>Gold (6,500+ points):&nbsp;</strong>Enjoy all Silver benefits, plus&nbsp;early access to new products.<strong><br><br>Diamond (10,000+ points):&nbsp;</strong>Enjoy all Gold benefits, plus eligibility to redeem specific products (e.g., tower fans) and invitations to VIP events.<strong>\n<br><br>Blue Diamond (13,999+ points):&nbsp;</strong>Enjoy all Diamond benefits, plus opportunities for brand ambassador collaboration, entry into the annual DELLA Gala grand prize draw, and&nbsp;access to product trials.\n",
        "pf_5542c735_value": "Email Della&nbsp;Customer Service at <u>manufacturer@dellahome.com.</u><br><br>Prohibited malicious registrations\n<br><br>• False information: Creating accounts with fake names, addresses, email addresses, or other personal data is strictly forbidden.\n<br><br>• Multiple accounts: One user may not register multiple accounts to obtain extra rewards or discounts, including using different emails or identities.\n<br><br>• Automated registration: Using bots, scripts, or any automated tools for bulk sign-ups is prohibited.\n<br><br>• Other malicious behavior: Exploiting system vulnerabilities or engaging in fraudulent transactions—or any conduct deemed malicious—is strictly prohibited.",
        "pf_66269714_value": "Your accumulated points can be used for:<br>\n<br>Checkout Discount:&nbsp;Directly offset the total order amount during checkout on our website or app.\n<br><br>Reward Redemption:&nbsp;Use points to redeem DELLA-branded merchandise, DELLA Gift Cards, or partner gift cards in the Rewards Center.<br><br><strong>Important Usage Notes:</strong>\n<br><br>Points are non-transferable and cannot be exchanged for cash.\n<br><br>Minimum point thresholds and per-order redemption limits may apply.\n<br><br>Return Policy:&nbsp;If you return an order for&nbsp;which you used points for a discount, the redeemed points will be refunded to your account.",
        "pf_ce31f842_value": "Validity Period:&nbsp;Yes, points have a validity period starting from the date they are credited. Unused points will automatically expire and be cleared upon reaching their expiry date. The current standard validity period is&nbsp;24 months. Please refer to the specific rules in your account notifications or official announcements.\n<br><br>Checking Your Balance:&nbsp;You can log into your account center on the DELLA website to view your real-time point balance, as well as a complete history of point earnings and redemptions.",
        "pf_1e30b1de_value": "To ensure fairness, the following actions are strictly prohibited. Violations may result in point forfeiture, reward revocation, account closure, or legal action:\n<br><br><first-sel>Providing false personal or registration information.\n<br><br>Registering multiple accounts to obtain improper rewards.\n<br><br>Using bots, scripts, or automated methods to participate in activities.\n<br><br>Exploiting Program vulnerabilities or engaging in fraudulent transactions.</first-sel>",
        "pf_94ccea5e_value": "If an order is returned, any points earned from that order will be deducted.\n<br><br>As mentioned above, if points were used to discount an order that is later returned, the used points will be refunded to your account.\n<br><br>DELLA is not responsible for any impact on your membership tier status that may result from point deductions or refunds due to order returns.",
        "pf_4a4b4e84_value": "If you have any questions regarding these terms, please contact the DELLA Customer Service Department at:&nbsp;<strong>manufacturer@dellahome.com.</strong>\n<br><br>Your participation in this Program signifies your agreement to DELLA's Privacy Policy, which governs how we collect and use your personal information to administer the Program.",
        "pf_e620e827_value": "You can join for free by registering for an account on the official DELLA website (dellahome.com)&nbsp;or via our mobile application.Simply provide your name, email address, and set a password. The Program is currently for personal, non-commercial use only.",
        "pf_db70a7d9_value": "Use your credits as Wallet-ready value at checkout.<br><br>100 Credits = $1 in savings&nbsp;on any Della purchase.\n<br><br>Get exclusive products, and enjoy premium benefits.",
        "pf_9cfdf959_value": "Join our community, engage with Della and earn redeemable points for exclusive rewards",
